    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This exceptional vehicle is in truly mint condition \u2014 a rare find in the used-car market. The exterior is flawless, with absolutely no scratches, dents, or paint imperfections of any kind. The interior looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor, with pristine upholstery, spotless carpeting, and every surface in perfect condition. Mechanically, this car is in outstanding shape \u2014 all systems function perfectly, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, and there are no warning lights, leaks, or concerns whatsoever. Service records are complete and up to date, and the vehicle has been meticulously maintained throughout its life. If you are looking for a used car that feels essentially new, this is it. Come see it in person and you will not be disappointed.",
      "price": 45000.0,
