      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 Budget-Friendly Project Car \u2014 Honest Listing, Real Opportunity! \ud83d\udd27 Looking for a fixer-upper or a parts vehicle? This car could be just what you need! We want to be completely upfront: this vehicle is in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and/or cosmetic work to get it road-ready. It has visible wear, known mechanical issues, and is best suited for a handy buyer, a hobbyist, or someone looking for parts. That said, it's priced to reflect exactly what it is \u2014 no surprises, no games. If you've got the skills or the patience, there's potential here at a price that won't break the bank. Come take a look and decide for yourself!",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in poor condition \u2014 buyers should be fully aware of what they're getting before making any decisions. The exterior shows significant wear, including multiple scratches, dents, and paint chips throughout the body panels. The interior has notable damage including worn and torn upholstery, damaged trim pieces, and general deterioration from heavy use. Mechanically, the car has known issues that will likely require meaningful repair work, and it is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project vehicle, or needs basic transportation and is comfortable with the associated risks. We strongly recommend a pre-purchase inspection by an independent mechanic before committing to this purchase. Priced accordingly to reflect its true condition.",
      "price": 5500.0,
